window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Did you know that one date can change everything?</p> <p>I’m not talking about the Disney fairy tale date where bunnies fly out your ass and butterflies break into song. I’m talking about a date where you don’t even know you’re on a date until the guy kisses you.</p> <p>Did I mention I thought I was straight back then? And that I had no clue he was gay? How was I ever that clueless. OMG! I nearly passed out. I mean, after we got naked and . . . Over the next few years, my whole world changed. I went from never-do-anything-wrong preacher’s kid to a wild child sowing his oats.</p> <p>Man, I loved oats . . . or men . . . if men were oats.This series is my story. You might find it hard to believe, but it’s all true. It’s also hilarious and heartwarming and sad (but only in spots) and uplifting . . . Did I mention funny? It’s really funny.You’re going to laugh your hiney off!</p>"; 
